.Dd $Mdocdate: April 27 2008 $
.Dt ACPITHINKPAD 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm acpithinkpad
.Nd IBM/Lenovo ThinkPad ACPI support
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "acpithinkpad* at acpi?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides ACPI support for IBM/Lenovo ThinkPad laptops.
It responds to various hotkey button presses such as the brightness adjustment
and wireless toggle keys.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr acpi 4 ,
.Xr intro 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 4.4 .
@


1.1
log
@add acpithinkpad(4), an acpi support driver for ibm/lenovo
thinkpads.

provides functionality that the bios did on older, non-acpi
thinkpads like respond to screen brightness keys and toggle the
bluetooth device on and off.

